{"_id":"indexed-weakness","name":"Indexed Weakness","type":"feat","img":"modules/cyberpunk-npcs/assets/items/indexed-weakness.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Activation:</strong> Bonus Action</p><p>Spend 1 ki point to mark a visible creature within 60 feet for 1 minute.</p><ul><li>While marked, your <strong>unarmed strikes</strong> against that creature deal <strong>extra force damage equal to your Wisdom modifier</strong>, once per turn.</li><li>The effect ends early if the target drops to 0 HP or you fall unconscious.</li></ul><p>Only monks can attune to this item, which appears as a glowing circuit tattoo that pulses when channeling ki.</p>"},"activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1},"duration":{"value":60,"units":"seconds"},"target":{"value":1,"type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"actionType":"other","damage":{"parts":[]},"requirements":"Monk","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"equipped":false,"attunement":1,"identified":true,"rarity":"rare","type":{"value":"tattoo","subtype":""}},"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":70,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.1","coreVersion":"13","createdTime":1748390000000,"modifiedTime":1748390000000,"lastModifiedBy":"GM"}}
{"_id":"perfect-loop","name":"Perfect Loop","type":"feat","img":"modules/cyberpunk-npcs/assets/items/perfect-loop.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Perfect Loop</strong>: Spend 1 <strong>Monk Focus</strong> point to immediately repeat your last action — whether it was an attack, ability check, or special feature.</p><p><strong>No need to re-roll any dice</strong> — the outcome is exactly the same. This ability reflects a moment of flawless execution, a perfect echo through the loop of combat.</p><p>Only monks can attune to this item.</p>"},"activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"actionType":"other","damage":{"parts":[]},"requirements":"Monk","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"equipped":false,"attunement":1,"identified":true,"rarity":"rare","type":{"value":"tattoo","subtype":""}},"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":80,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.1","coreVersion":"13","createdTime":1748391000000,"modifiedTime":1748391000000,"lastModifiedBy":"GM"}}
{"_id":"shared-circuit","name":"Shared Circuit","type":"feat","img":"modules/cyberpunk-npcs/assets/items/shared-circuit.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Shared Circuit</strong>: Spend 1 <strong>Monk Focus</strong> point to link yourself to an ally within 30 ft for 1 minute. While linked:</p><ul><li>You can use your reaction to take half the damage they would take (rounded down).</li><li>If they drop to 0 HP, you may transfer your own HP to them as a reaction (up to your monk level).</li></ul><p>Only monks can attune to this item.</p>"},"activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1},"duration":{"value":60,"units":"seconds"},"target":{"value":1,"type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"actionType":"other","damage":{"parts":[]},"requirements":"Monk","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"equipped":false,"attunement":1,"identified":true,"rarity":"rare","type":{"value":"tattoo","subtype":""}},"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":90,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.1","coreVersion":"13","createdTime":1748392000000,"modifiedTime":1748392000000,"lastModifiedBy":"GM"}}
{"_id":"pulse-sync-burst","name":"Pulse-Sync Burst","type":"feat","img":"modules/cyberpunk-npcs/assets/items/pulse-sync-burst.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Pulse-Sync Burst</strong>: Spend 1 <strong>Monk Focus</strong> point to sync with 2 or more allies you can see. For 1 round:</p><ul><li>All synced characters (including you) gain +10 ft movement.</li><li>If any of you Dash or use an unarmed strike, you gain temporary HP equal to your Wisdom modifier.</li></ul><p>Only monks can attune to this item.</p>"},"activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1},"duration":{"value":6,"units":"seconds"},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"range":{"value":30,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"actionType":"other","damage":{"parts":[]},"requirements":"Monk","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"equipped":false,"attunement":1,"identified":true,"rarity":"rare","type":{"value":"tattoo","subtype":""}},"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":100,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.1","coreVersion":"13","createdTime":1748393000000,"modifiedTime":1748393000000,"lastModifiedBy":"GM"}}
{"_id":"care-protocol-override","name":"Care Protocol Override","type":"feat","img":"modules/cyberpunk-npcs/assets/items/care-protocol-override.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Care Protocol Override</strong>: Twice per short rest, you may:</p><ul><li>Heal 1d4 HP</li><li>Remove frightened or charmed</li><li>Stabilize a creature</li></ul><p>If the target takes damage within 1 round, you may impose disadvantage on that attack or effect as a reaction.</p><p>✦ You may spend 1 <strong>Monk Focus</strong> point to heal an additional 1d4 HP when using this ability.</p><p>Only monks can attune to this item.</p>"},"activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1},"duration":{"value":6,"units":"seconds"},"target":{"value":1,"type":"creature"},"range":{"value":30,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":2,"max":2,"per":"sr"},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"actionType":"other","damage":{"parts":[]},"requirements":"Monk","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"equipped":false,"attunement":1,"identified":true,"rarity":"rare","type":{"value":"tattoo","subtype":""}},"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":110,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.1","coreVersion":"13","createdTime":1748394000000,"modifiedTime":1748394000000,"lastModifiedBy":"GM"}}
{"_id":"harmonic-bloom","name":"Harmonic Bloom","type":"feat","img":"modules/cyberpunk-npcs/assets/items/harmonic-bloom.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Harmonic Bloom</strong>: Spend 1 <strong>Monk Focus</strong> point to enter a 3-turn trance. While chanting:</p><ul><li>You and allies within 10 ft gain +2 AC and saving throws.</li><li>At the end of the 3rd turn, if you’re still conscious, allies in range heal 1d4 HP and you regain 1 Monk Focus.</li></ul><p>Only monks can attune to this item.</p>"},"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1},"duration":{"value":18,"units":"seconds"},"target":{"value":null,"type":""},"range":{"value":10,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"actionType":"other","damage":{"parts":[]},"requirements":"Monk","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false},"equipped":false,"attunement":1,"identified":true,"rarity":"rare","type":{"value":"tattoo","subtype":""}},"flags":{},"folder":null,"sort":120,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.2.1","coreVersion":"13","createdTime":1748395000000,"modifiedTime":1748395000000,"lastModifiedBy":"GM"}}
